\par The first vociferous defenders of this notion appeared at the beginning of the 1970s. Two American paleontologists, }{\b\fs22\cf1\insrsid9903380\charrsid9903380 Niles Eldredge and Stephen Jay Gould,}{\fs22\cf1\insrsid9903380\charrsid9903380 
