\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sb100\sa100\sbauto1\saauto1\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid9903380 {\fs22\cf1\insrsid9903380\charrsid9903380 Allah creates our perception of time. Allah,
